profile: Paul's Restorations is a family owned and operated Corporate business celebrating 35 years of successful growth and diversity.  Specialized Project Managers with proven dedication and successful representation in handling all sizes of claims in Fire, Flood and disaster damage restoration services. We also offer mould and asbestos remediation, fire and smoke clean up and storm response services. We take care of cleaning up any water leak with our extraction service and state of the art drying systems. We can help you to remove all the water, dry your carpets, floors, walls and furniture to restore your home or office to its original condition or even better. We perform restoration services for both residential and commercial properties. It is our commitment to you, the home owner that your needs are met and that the process of getting your home back to the way it was is seamless and with the least amount of disruption to you and your family.  Paul's Restorations will take complete care of you and guide you through the entire process of getting your property back to normal as quickly as possible
